For an updated version of the original FastaSeqStats tool to obtain basic statistics from a FASTA file, please check:
https://github.com/kikelg/FastaSeqStats

GenoToolBox:
============

GenoToolBox is a collection of scripts used to manipulate genomic data from
simple fasta sequences (for example fasta_extract) to create gene models based
in a reference genome (for example genemodeler).
